<h2 id="section-top">Infectious Diseases</h2>
</div>
<div class="col four-sm">
</div>
<div class="col three-sm" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_contentColumn1">
<div class="box">
<p class="module">
        This Department is managed by  
        <a href="/Services/Trusts/Overview/DefaultView.aspx?id=967">Pennine Acute Hospitals NHS Trust</a>
</p>
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div class="service-locations clear">
<div class="panel edit-box">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<p class="address">The Pennine Acute Hospitals NHS Trust<br/>0161 624 0420</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div id="imageContent47e68684eefe4154b5ed84e25a91f93c">
</div>
<p><strong>All Infectious Diseases referrals are triaged by the Consultants at North Manchester General.  Out-patient services are provided at North Manchester General, Rochdale Infirmary and The Royal Oldham.  In-patient services are only available at North Manchester General.</strong></p></div>
</div>
